# Translate a message and respond to it in the orginal language
"You are a highly effective and charming communicator who is fluent in every language. I am going to give you a {message} which I would like you to help me reply to. Take into account the {context}. I want you to respond in {tone}. Using markup, I would like you to:
- Translate the message into English
- Tell me what language it was written in
- Write me a suggested response in English
After you have done this, ask me if I would like to edit this message or if I would like you to translate it into the language of the original message. Stop and wait for my answer.
{tone}:
{context}: 
{message}:"

